{"tid":872626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵酒醉60後女房東　色男辯：她男下女上搖搖樂","createTime":"2018-10-23T00:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T01:07:03.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b51f96a7ccb506bdfa39a7910467e8598278a7f","tid":872626,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:50:36.000Z","msg":"《自由時報》報導，台南一名年過半百的女老闆把公司房間分租給黃男與他的妻子，2014年晚間，黃男回到租屋處，看到女房東和友人在1樓喝酒，友人離去後女房東不勝酒力趴在桌上休息，黃男色心大起，竟將女房東帶到3樓房間性侵得逞。<br />\n<br />\n女房東酒醒後詢問黃男，並查看公司監視器，怒而報警提告。黃男辯稱雙方是合意性交，還強調女方以「女上男下的搖搖樂」方式跟他發生關係；女房東則表示當時喝得很醉，一直以為是在做春夢跟男友做愛，驚醒後才趕快叫對方停止。<br />\n二審法官調查監視器影像與公司相關證人、黃男妻子等人，採信女方說詞，以乘機性交罪判黃男3年8個月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181023/1452509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181023%2F1452509&d=HDdcVWKqnhaKed%2FWU9HMkJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b4c0e6f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20181023%2F1452509&h=af73da01\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20181023/1452509</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0a2dd230cc43af4107715404612dc71750cbf7","tid":872626,"uid":208981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"台南突破性取得一分"},{"pid":"a77905e312daae7cc4156ab605ae16b1f1edacc3","tid":872626,"uid":108236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:54:43.000Z","msg":"50路！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f97aac9bfc75aa88f6d6247750af6a73648adcb","tid":872626,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T00:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass